E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Clay, I've run into some trouble on the East Borough bridge.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~Clay，我在东区大桥上遇到了麻烦。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Not in the van, baby. But maybe I'm interested in what's in the back of it.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~货车不重要，宝贝。我对车上的货更感兴趣一些。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Are you a, a motorcycle club like us and the Angels of Death?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你们是...我们和死亡天使那样的机车俱乐部吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Couple of friends and I are in a fix, Terry. You down?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我和几个朋友遇到了些麻烦，Terry。你能来吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I do, I do. There's a van that's in the wrong hands, if you catch my drift.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~缺的，缺的。有一辆货车落到了坏人手里，懂我意思吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Guess they wouldn't be top hookers if they couldn't.
~z~Yo, wait. Don't I recognise you? Wait a minute, wait a minute...
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~哟，等下。我好像认识你？我想想，我再想想...

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-Fuck you. ~n~Make yourself useful and clean this shit up.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－操你妈。~n~－发挥点作用好吗？过来收拾干净。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Boys, meet Malcolm. He's with the Uptown Riders. Malc, these are two of the most real brothers in The Lost MC.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟们，他是Malcolm。Malc，这二位是失落帮最棒的兄弟。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I think we better take a cage on this run.
~z~You know how it is can't trust nothing these days. Can't trust the price of gas,
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你也懂的，现在啥都信不过啊。油价信不过，

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I mean, you heard about the credit crunch? It's crunching underneath my feet.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~那个，听说过信贷危机吗？已经塌到我家了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-What you waitin' for, the bus?~n~-This is not a fuckin' parade.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－愣着干嘛，等公交呢？~n~－这又不是花车游行。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~hold up where you think you're going man?
~z~They teach you boys how to play with the big dogs in The Lost MC? I hope so. 'Cause this bitch bite back.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你们失落帮教不教怎么耍大狗？最好教过。这狗脾气暴。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Well, with these cops sniffing around we might all be gone soon.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~现在条子查得严，哪天我们就都进去了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Or why you guys look like rejects from a bondage club.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~也别提为啥你们都像是被SM俱乐部拒之门外的顾客。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~It ain't how The Lost MC roll either. See you round, man.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~失落帮也不是这样的。再见了，兄弟。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~You really want me to shoot you?
~z~God damn, Johnny. All that shit gone to waste. We ain't even gonna get paid now.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~妈个逼的，Johnny。全他妈白干了。这下钱都拿不到了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~You gonna pay my bills and put food on the table?
~z~Shit, I could swear you was on that show - America's Next Top Hooker.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，你肯定上过那个节目——《美国新花魁》。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~What's up with you guys and the Angels of Death?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你们和死亡天使是怎么回事？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~This is one serious gun, amigo. This what they call a street sweeper?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~这可是硬家伙啊，兄弟。该不会是传说中的「清道夫」吧？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, man. I'm cool. Just holla if you need any help now.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~没事，兄弟，我很好。就是不知道你好不好。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Cause, man, I mean - I met some of these Angels of Death and they're some real unfortunate sons-a-bitches.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~因为，老兄，我也见过几个死亡天使，都是些倒霉催的逼玩意。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~That's about accurate for this shit. It'll carve through any motherfuckers dumb enough to stand down wind of us.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~名副其实啊。谁敢跟我们对着干，骨灰都给他扬喽。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Malc, man, get one of your boys to bring our wheels to the drop off.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~Malc，兄弟，你派个人把我们的车送过去。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~True that, cat. Ay oh, E. Let him know what it is.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~没错，老弟。对了，E，跟他说下计划。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~You're doing great, honey. It's okay, just come with me.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你做得很棒，宝贝。没事了，有我在呢。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~True, man, true. Shit gets colder every day. I'll see you round.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~是啊，兄弟，没错。现在一天比一天凉。我们以后见。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~We ain't hanging round man. Get up in this van, okay?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~此地不宜久留，老兄。快点上车好吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~No doubt, drop that bitch like she hot. The bitch has dropped.
~z~Some assholes are about to run into trouble at the toll booth. Can you assist?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我们要在收费站给某些傻逼准备一个惊喜。你能来帮忙吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Well, we should do something about that. See you soon.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~那我们不能坐视不理啊。待会儿见。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Either of you blow up the van, you'll be back to prospecting.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~谁把货车打炸了，就滚回见习期吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Man, I don't know. What is worth it? Sticking our heads out to steal a truck of blow for a few thousand bucks?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟，我不知道。又有什么是值得的？~n~拿命去偷一车白粉，赚几千块钱值吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-Turn around now...~n~-Hey look, I got some change right here.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－请回吧...~n~－喂，听着，我这儿有零钱。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Like you guys used to be. Back in about what, '63 or something?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~就跟以前的你们一样。多久以前来着，63年左右吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~We've still got heart, man. The Lost MC are still here. We just don't get on MeTV and scream about it.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我们的热血还在，兄弟。失落帮依然存在。只是我们不会上电视喊出来而已。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~We best use a car here, brother. Come on.
~z~My bust. I didn't mean to make light of that Johnny.
~z~Okay, I guess all we gotta worry about is the cops taking us down then?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~那好，看来我们只需要担心找上门的条子了？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~about the merits of good American machinery versus foreign plastic fantastic crap.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~美国重机和塑料洋垃圾的好坏优劣上吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Me and some boys are about to ambush a convoy on the East Borough. You down?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我们准备在东区大桥埋伏一个车队。你来吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~So, Malcolm, I got a question for you.
~z~How you and me gonna let them mother fuckers take us like that? I'm bigger than that, I'm bigger.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我俩怎么就让他们骑到头上了？我不服啊，老子不服。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~What was all this shit with you dissing me in front of Elizabeta, man?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你在Elizabeta面前说我那么多坏话干嘛，老兄？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Now get the fuck out of here.
~z~Maybe he's the lucky one. So long, Johnny.
~z~Racism, misogyny, bad personal hygiene. But still, why you wanna kill each other?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~搞歧视，搞仇女，不讲个人卫生。~n~但是，你们互相残杀干嘛？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I'm going to take care of this, we're going to get through this.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~这边我来解决，我们一定能挺过去的。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I'm always down to help a brother in need.
~z~You might just get me angry, you hear.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~叔叔我啊，可是真的要生气了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Come on, Johnny. Pull your weight, yeah?
~z~But you can't be a bigger mope than the last two fuckups Liz Torres had me partying with.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~只是你总比之前Liz Torres给我派的那俩扫把星好。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Let's keep a low profile and ride in a car, man.
~z~Dude, can one of your people bring the bikes around?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~老兄，能让你的手下把摩托备好吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Yo, Johnny boy, I got a question for you, if you got the inclination to answer.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~哟，Johnny仔。我想问你一个问题，不知道你有没有兴趣回答。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, you was like John number four or some shit. Right?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你是不是那个什么阿强四号，对吧？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Fuck me. This is an American firearm.
~z~We been kicking ass way longer than you young bucks, that's for sure.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我们老江湖可比你们这些小弟弟老道多了，还用想吗。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Hell, they going to want even more product when they lose their jobs
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~再说，工作一丢，需求量不还得噌噌往上涨，

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I don't know. Lost count, son.
~z~I'm always down to help a brother in need.
~z~ Yeah, yeah, yeah. Can you let me through?
~z~Can you get your people to bring our bikes to the drop-off?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你能找个手下帮我们备好摩托吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~It's the personal hygiene thing. We're real sticklers for cleanliness in The Lost MC.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~因为他们不讲卫生。我们失落帮的人都有洁癖。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Fraid not, Liz. Traffic's flowin' just fine. Your friend got wherever they was goin'.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~并没有，Liz。路况太好了，你的朋友已经无影无踪了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~You guys all met? Malc, these are my boys. Gentlemen, this is Malcolm.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你们认识吗？Malc，他们是我的兄弟。兄弟们，这位是Malcolm。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~It's impossible to find good help in this city.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~想在自由城找到好帮手太难了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-You're holding traffic up. What's the problem?~n~-Hey, we're kind of in a rush here, okay?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－后面都被你堵住了，有病吧？~n~－喂，我们赶时间，好吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Malc, man, you look good in that booth. You should think about a second career.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~Malc，老兄，你管收费站还挺像样的。有没有考虑过转行？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Well, it's serious business. I lost a lot of brothers. Killed a lot of men, too.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我没在开玩笑。我失去了很多兄弟，还杀了很多人。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I mean, what's Bohan got? Give me a good reason why you wanna go to Bohan.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~真的，Bohan有什么？能解释下你们为什么要来Bohan吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Back off of him, you stupid shit.
~z~You going make me lose my mind.
~z~-It's my job. ~n~What up, Johnny boy? We talked to your girl.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－职责所在。~n~－还好吗，Johnny仔？我跟这姑娘谈过了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Hey, I can't be to sure but this looks like one of those fake bills I've been hearing about.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~喂，我也不太确定，但这个看着像是那种假钞啊。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~These guys ain't gonna know what hit 'em.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~他们不会知道自己是怎么死的。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~They bribed a guard on the East Borough Bridge to let 'em through without checking their load, right?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~他们贿赂了东区大桥的边检员，直接放行不用检查，对吧？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I don't wanna take you to hospital, man. Get in cover.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我不想送你去医院，老兄。找掩护。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Ha ha. Don't think I would have been on the outside long enough to sell it anyway. Don't get arrested, Johnny.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~哈哈。就算我有命拿到货，估计也没命卖了。你可别被抓了，Johnny。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~The products more important than you are, you assholes.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~车上的货比你们的命值钱多了，混蛋们。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I can handle motherfucker. She's just one cold female. And I don't want her thinking I'm a bitch.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我圆你妈逼。她是那种冷血女人，我不想让她把我当婊子。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-You've got to be kidding me. What's the problem?~n~-It's okay, you just breathe.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－你跟我这儿开什么玩笑，有病吧？~n~－没事的，深呼吸。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~and show them I'm a bitch, but I ain't their fucking bitch, okay?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~让他们知道老娘就是婊子，但不是他们能惹的婊子，懂？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-You got to hold up in here, I'm talking to you alright?~n~-Johnny!
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－不许再前进了，乖乖照做懂吧？~n~－Johnny！

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~can't trust this President for sure, and you know you can't even trust this money.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~总统肯定信不过，就连钞票都信不过了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~We're about to see what we're made of, people.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~马上就要掏出真本事了，各位。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Take us to the Point, Johnny. We got a lockup there.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~带我们去Chase Point，Johnny。我们的车库在那儿。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Hey, dude, I'm sorry. Your brother's gonna be remembered.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~喂，老兄，我很抱歉。我们会记住你兄弟的。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Uh huh. This fool called Playboy X and some off the boat European. No surprise, the deal went to shit.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~啊哈。一个叫Playboy X的傻逼，加一个初来乍到的欧洲人。意料之内，交易真吹了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Shit, man. Always carry exact change. I'll be there soon.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，兄弟。让你出门不带硬币。我马上就来。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Man, Clay, you psychic or something? But this will be worth your while, Brother.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我去，Clay，你是会读心术吗？这次来了就是赚到，兄弟。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Aight, go ahead, go ahead. Let's go.
~z~Look, I will come back with all the exact change that you need.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~听着，回来的时候我会把钱一分不差地交给你。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~What is it about sitting in little booths and wearing uniforms that turns guys into assholes?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~穿着皇协军的衣服坐在收费站里是种怎样的体验？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, I thought you and your friends were the real deal. Shows how wrong I can be.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，我还以为你和你的朋友真有本事。看来我看错人了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-You're holding up traffic. What's the problem here?
~z~You gotta take some thieving, snitching motherfuckers
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你要对付的是几个偷窃告发的混蛋，

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~A'ight, this one's on us. Now move your ass.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，现在由我们接管。你们走吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Completely fucking lost, if you ask me.
~z~I got kids I can't even claim. The government gone and fucked us good. You know it, you know it, I know you know it.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我都不能跟孩子相认。政府跑了，我们受苦。你懂的，你一定懂的，我知道你懂。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-Don't worry about it. ~n~-I'm supposed to protect you, okay?
~z~I don't know. The alternative seems kind of lame too. Going straight.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~不知道。说实话，都没好到哪去吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~This ain't happening, Liz. We're a man down.
~z~Got some bad news, Liz. That van ain't going anywhere. Sorry.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~有个坏消息，Liz。货车开不回来了。抱歉。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~You guys is gonna go down there and tear 'em apart.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~你们只需要过去，把他们撕成碎片。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~It ain't how uptown riders roll. You understand, man. Shit ain't right.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~上城骑士也不是这样的。知道吗，兄弟？不太对劲啊。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~What's the big deal about Bohan anyways? Bohan ain't shit, that's for sure.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~Bohan有什么好的？Bohan屁都不是，大实话。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-Honey. It's okay, just breathe.~n~-Listen to me man, you gotta get outta the way.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－宝贝，没事的，深呼吸。~n~－听我说，伙计，麻烦你让路。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~It's just part of our vibe man, roll with it.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~是我们独有的风格，兄弟，试试吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-Aaargh, ahh!~n~-Come on, let's get this shit moving.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－啊，啊啊啊！~n~－好了，这下就不堵车了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I don't know. I mean, we ride bikes and we ride them hard. But the thing is
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~不知道。就是...我们玩摩托，也玩得很深。但问题是，

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, yeah, you're good to go. You're good, go, go.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~好好，你们走吧。没问题，走吧走吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~It's good to roll with you, Malc. Not that we know each other too well.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~跟你一起干活真好，Malc。倒不是因为我俩很熟，

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Look, you don't got exact change, you're not going through.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~听着，不把五块钱拿出来，你别想过去。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Hey Johnny, you and them Lost bikers ain't that bad.
~z~Yeah, I did and it handled like a piece of shit. I dumped it in the lockup you mentioned, if you're interested.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~到手了，驾驶手感跟屎一样。已经扔到你说的车库了，随你喜欢吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Seems like everybody here wants to come through this here little gate.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~好像一个个的都想从这个小门过去啊。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Things can't be going too well for you if you heading to Bohan. Am I right?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~都要往Bohan跑了，那你们也不会好到哪去。没说错吧？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~We got a lockup on the Point, man. Come on.
~z~There's a war. Stupid shit, but very violent.
~z~Good thing that little family didn't come through here five minutes later.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~幸好这小俩口来得早，否则就出事了。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~That's all the shit that happens in Bohans. Death and a dripping dick.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~Bohan就这点特产。鸡儿梆硬和尸骨冰凉，真的。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Sure, Malc. I'm just hoping you, me and Liz can stay outta jail long enough to enjoy it. Later on.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~是啊，Malc。但愿你、我，还有Liz能在进去之前把这笔钱用完。回见。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Come on, Johnny. Ease up on that van.
~z~Stay on the van. Stay on the van, you dicks.
~z~Plenty of mediocre hookers out here I guess. You really got to be on some dick sucking skill level to be on the top.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~现在妓女都烂大街了吧。口活不好还真不能夺魁。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~It just a shame he gonna be remembered for a stick up gone wrong. Yo, peace out Johnny.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~只可惜对他最后的印象是一场失败的抢劫。哟，再见了，Johnny。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Hell, looking at the two of you don't make no sense to me.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~天，你俩能站在一起简直不可思议。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Joking aside, man. Is this shit worth it?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~说正经的，老兄。开战真的值得吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Remember the classes, okay? Would you just let us through?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~课上教过的吧？麻烦你放我们过去好吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Aight now, try not to do too much damage with this here, aight?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，别拿这个搞出太大动静，好吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, sure you are. Whatever you say, Johnny boy.
~z~I didn't think you Lost bikers got down with peoples like Malc here.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~没想到你们失落帮还能跟Malc这种人走到一块儿去。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Then I guess you got to prove yourself. No pressure, man.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~那你得支棱起来啊。别有压力，兄弟。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, did you get rid of that stupid bike of yours and drive my van for me?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，你那傻逼摩托车扔了没？我的货车到手了吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~and one of my upstanding business associates?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~谁是我优秀的生意合伙人吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Sorry, sorry, it's my first day. This might take a minute.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉，抱歉，今天刚上岗。可能有点慢哈。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, how's traffic flow. Did the right people get held up on their way to Bohan?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，路况如何？在来Bohan的路上拦住该拦住的人了没？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Enough of this shit, just let me through, okay?
~z~You want to get the clap or some shit? You want to get shot?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~想过来啪啪啪吗？还是想挨枪子儿？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~"There's a war." You sounding all dramatic and shit.
~z~Or, why you guys dress like the Republican Space Rangers.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~也别提为啥你们打扮的像《共和太空游骑兵》。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Them with their sports bikes, you with your choppers.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~他们喜欢骑跑车，你们喜欢巡航车。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Can't you tell the difference between a narc
~z~we don't wear fancy dresses or do pinky finger shakes or anything like that. So I ain't sure what that makes us.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我们不穿奇装异服，也不勾指起誓。我也不太确定这样算什么种类。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Go for the convoy. Give it everything.
~z~Yeah, I can tell with them clean crisp threads you wearing, Johnny.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~确实，看你这身干净的衣服就知道了，Johnny。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~People always gonna want what we got to sell.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~他们哪天不想要我们的货了？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Are you really wasting my time like this? Come on.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~能别浪费我的时间了吗？快点。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Those are the rules, I don't make 'em, but I stick to 'em.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~规矩就是规矩，不是我定的，但我得遵守。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, man. The vibe. It's how we do. You know we a complete subculture.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~对，兄弟。风格。就是我们的作风。毕竟我们是一种亚文化。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I'll send Andreas to check it out. See you soon.
~z~Anyway, what I'm asking is, what's the deal with this music you put out and the branded clothing and shit?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~总之，我要问一下，你现在放的音乐跟这个品牌服装是什么情况？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~You ain't hiding from this gun, bitches!
~z~Well, Malcolm, it's your crew. The Uptown Riders.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~那个，Malcolm，是关于你们的，上城骑士。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I'm guessing Liz wants this convoy hit like a fucking freight train if this is the firepower she's dishing out.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~都掏出这种大家伙了，看来Liz很看重这次的袭击啊。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Okay, okay, but you know what, I'm gonna need some rubber gloves.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~好，好。就是那个...能给双橡胶手套吗？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~I can't take care of my mortgage, you know I got me kids.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~我都还不起贷款了，家里还有孩子。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Man can those bitches suck on a dick!
~z~We're after the van. Go easy on it.
~z~Whoo, well now, that's a fine little nest egg to get us through a low point in these here global markets, baby.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~呜！好了，这笔钱应该能帮我们撑过这段萧条时期了，宝贝。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~That's the van we're trying to steal, John.
~z~-So just turn around and head on back to Dukes for me, will ya?~n~-Are you kidding me?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－请你调头开回Dukes吧，好吗？~n~－开什么玩笑？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~-You can compromise these nuts. Gimme some. ~n~-Shit, these ain't troubling times for us.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~－你妥协个鸡巴。击个拳。~n~－妈的，我们这行又没萧条。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Shit, man. Always carry exact change. I'll be there soon.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，兄弟。让你出门不带硬币。我马上就来。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Oh aight, so, like, it's like one of those gang wars they have out there in Los Santos, or something?
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~好吧。那什么，是不是跟洛圣都那边的帮派战争差不多？

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~And in this troubling economic climate, you gotta make compromises.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~在这种经济大环境下，人不得不妥协啊。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Take us to the bridge, Johnny boy.
~z~We need to get this van out of here. Get in, man.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~赶紧把货车开回去。上车，兄弟。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~Hey fellas. No time for introductions. Let's get it on.
E1E1AUD.translated: ~z~伙计们，没空介绍你们认识了。开干吧。

E1E1AUD.original: ~z~So let's not let this descend into an argument
~z~Don't blow up the van. That's what we're after.
